
The Game.
Welcome to The Game; if you already know about the game, congratulations on losing The Game. If you are unaware, here are the rules:
Do NOT think about The Game.
If you think about The Game, you lose.
Once you stop thinking about The Game after losing The Game, The Game resets.
Everyone who knows of The Game is playing The Game.
That now includes you.
When you lose The Game, feel free to induct others into The Game or cause them to lose The Game.
The only way to win The Game is to no longer be able to precieve or comprehend The Game.
Until the day comes that your brain no longer functions, have no choice but to play The Game and involuntarily lose The Game.
Enjoy

